summary: Just a pack of  presets for race menu
descriptionHtml:
[code]﻿[/code]Race menu presets for you to use. 

Need all required mods for the exact look. 

[added Asian preset as optional download] IF you want long hair like in screenshots you need [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/88416]THIS[/url]﻿
check image tab for more images
[added violet as optional download] This is a xboxones friends dark elf character that ive loved for awhile and really wanted to create. Credit to "that guy" lol 

UPDATE - someone told me they were getting purple body parts ( This is because im using a friends tattoo mod , and didnt think about them not showing ) He has allowed me to upload them as a optional download. So check optional downloads for that file. Thank you [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/44456462]Dark1Nova[/url] :) That way you can use the tattoos ive attached to a few presets or change them to your liking.
